      "type": "OperatingEnvelope",
      "name": "F1717 compression-bending operating envelope",
      "description": "Static axial compressive force 0–2500 N applied at 10°±0.5° off-axis per ASTM F1717; crosshead displacement rate 5 mm/min ±0.5 mm/min; ambient temperature 22±3 °C; UHMWPE block density 0.93–0.96 g/cm³; screw insertion torque 6–8 N·m; test span 100 mm±1 mm between rod clamp centres. Cortical bone modulus surrogate 14±2 GPa. All 11 test specimens fell within these bounds."
    }
  },
