      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is a commercially validated FEA solver with ISO 9001 quality management. The FDA in-house code (FEBio 3.5) was verified against published benchmark problems. DePuy Synthes solver instance operates under a documented software quality plan including version control, regression testing, and change management. All three codes passed ASME V&V 10 benchmark suite relevant to contact-nonlinear structural problems.",
