      "rationale": "Code verification performed against NAFEMS LE1 and LE10 linear elastic benchmarks and a published nonlinear contact patch test. All three solver instances reproduced reference solutions within 0.5% for stress and displacement QoIs. FEBio additionally verified against Hertzian contact analytical solution (error < 0.3%).",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/ac/ncv",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Numerical code verification acceptance criterion",
