      "rationale": "Mesh convergence study conducted on three systematically refined meshes (coarse 18k, medium 72k, fine 288k hexahedral elements). Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI < 1.2% for stiffness and < 0.9% for yield force. Medium mesh selected for production runs; discretization error contribution to combined uncertainty is 0.8% of QoI.",
