      "rationale": "Continuum isotropic linear-elastic constitutive model for titanium alloy screw (Ti-6Al-4V) and UHMWPE block is appropriate for the pre-yield loading regime. Geometric nonlinearity (large displacement) activated for post-yield regime up to 40 mm. Contact formulation captures screw-block interaction. Model form uncertainty estimated at ±4% via comparison of three independent FEA implementations that share no common code.",
